subject: Re: URGENT: Cloud deployment failing - Mercury API not responding
message_body:
Dear John,

Thank you for contacting Aetheros Support. We understand the urgency of this issue and are committed to resolving it as quickly as possible.

We have identified a known issue with our cloud deployment system that may be causing the error you are experiencing. Our engineering team is currently working on a fix.

In the meantime, we recommend trying the following workaround:

1. Increase the timeout value for your API calls in your Mercury code.
2. Retry the deployment process.

Please try this workaround and let us know if you continue to experience issues. We will keep you updated on the status of the fix.

Sincerely,
The Aetheros Support Team
